                </div>
                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="name">카테고리 <br><span style="font-size: 0.7rem;">*카테고리를 선택해주세요.</span></div>
                    <div class="value">
                    <ul>
                        <li class="radio-btn"><input type="radio" id="category1" name="studyCategory" value="언어" required>
